channel.title: Help Please 317 Client
channel.description:
Hey, If someone can help me this will help heaps!! Well anyway....
I have a 317 Client name "HyBriD PvP" and on the top of the client screen it has has a drop box named "File" and under "File" is had "Vote, Fourms, doante" How do i remove them as they are opening someone else's links... Or how can i change them?
Thanks very much!! :)

item.title: Help Please 317 Client
item.dc:creator: @mista_pnut mista pnut
item.description:
@mista_pnut wrote:

Open one of the links, copy the url it takes you to. Use the z-filesearcher and put in that url, then go to it and change it to the url you would like. Not sure how much help that could be but, hope it works!
